# About page (explorer/templates/about.html)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
#: explorer/templates/about.html:6
msgid "Nosotros | ViveMedellín"
msgstr "About | ViveMedellín"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:10
msgid ""
"Descubre cómo ViveMedellín te ayuda a explorar la ciudad: filtros por zona, "
"tipos de lugares, búsqueda inteligente y datos verificados de restaurantes, "
"bares y experiencias."
msgstr ""
"Discover how ViveMedellín helps you explore the city: filters by area, place"
" types, smart search, and verified data for restaurants, bars, and "
"experiences."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:23
msgid "Tu guía local"
msgstr "Your local guide"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:26
msgid "Descubre Medellín<br><span class=\"title-accent\">como nunca antes</span>"
msgstr ""
"Discover Medellín<br><span class=\"title-accent\">like never before</span>"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:29
msgid ""
"ViveMedellín es un directorio curado de restaurantes, bares, rooftops y "
"experiencias en Medellín y sus alrededores. Organizamos la ciudad para que "
"encuentres lo que buscas, más rápido."
msgstr ""
"ViveMedellín is a curated directory of restaurants, bars, rooftops, and "
"experiences in Medellín and surrounding areas. We organize the city so you "
"can find what you're looking for, faster."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:37
msgid "¿Qué es ViveMedellín?"
msgstr "What is ViveMedellín?"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:47
msgid "Organizado por zonas reales"
msgstr "Organized by real areas"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:50
msgid ""
"Navega por comunas (El Poblado, Laureles, La Candelaria...) y pueblos "
"cercanos. Sin mapas genéricos—barrios reales."
msgstr ""
"Browse by comunas (El Poblado, Laureles, La Candelaria...) and nearby towns."
" No generic maps—real neighborhoods."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:61
msgid "Filtros inteligentes"
msgstr "Smart filters"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:64
msgid ""
"Filtra por tipo (restaurantes, bares, cafés, rooftops...) y características "
"(terraza, música en vivo, pet-friendly, delivery...)."
msgstr ""
"Filter by type (restaurants, bars, cafés, rooftops...) and features "
"(terrace, live music, pet-friendly, delivery...)."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:75
msgid "Búsqueda semántica"
msgstr "Semantic search"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:78
msgid ""
"Pregunta naturalmente: \"rooftop romántico en Poblado\" o \"café tranquilo "
"para trabajar\". Nuestra IA entiende tu intención."
msgstr ""
"Ask naturally: \"romantic rooftop in Poblado\" or \"quiet café to work\". "
"Our AI understands your intent."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:89
msgid "Cerca de mí"
msgstr "Near me"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:92
msgid ""
"Usa tu ubicación para encontrar lugares a poca distancia. Perfecto cuando ya"
" estás afuera explorando."
msgstr ""
"Use your location to find places within walking distance. Perfect when "
"you're already out exploring."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:103
msgid "Cómo usarlo"
msgstr "How to use it"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:106
msgid "Pasos para usar ViveMedellín"
msgstr "Steps to use ViveMedellín"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:110
msgid "Elige zona"
msgstr "Choose area"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:114
msgid "Añade filtros"
msgstr "Add filters"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:118
msgid "Explora"
msgstr "Explore"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:122
msgid "Decide"
msgstr "Decide"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:130
msgid "Parte de una zona"
msgstr "Start from an area"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:133
msgid ""
"Desde el home, haz clic en una burbuja de área (El Poblado, Laureles, "
"Envigado...) o usa el dropdown de Área para enfocar tu búsqueda en un barrio"
" específico."
msgstr ""
"From the home page, click an area bubble (El Poblado, Laureles, Envigado...)"
" or use the Area dropdown to focus your search on a specific neighborhood."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:141
msgid "Combina tipo + características"
msgstr "Combine type + features"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:144
msgid ""
"Selecciona un tipo de lugar (restaurantes, bares, cafés...) y afina con "
"características especiales como terraza, música en vivo, pet-friendly o "
"delivery."
msgstr ""
"Select a place type (restaurants, bars, cafés...) and refine with special "
"features like terrace, live music, pet-friendly, or delivery."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:152
msgid "Usa búsqueda semántica o Cerca de mí"
msgstr "Use semantic search or Near me"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:155
msgid ""
"Escribe una consulta natural como \"café tranquilo para trabajar\" o activa "
"Cerca de mí para encontrar lugares alrededor de tu ubicación actual."
msgstr ""
"Type a natural query like \"quiet café to work\" or activate Near me to find"
" places around your current location."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:163
msgid "Ve los detalles y ve"
msgstr "View details and go"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:166
msgid ""
"Abre \"Ver detalles\" para ver fotos, rango de precios, servicios y lugares "
"similares. Luego salta directamente a Google Maps o Waze."
msgstr ""
"Open \"View details\" to see photos, price range, services, and similar "
"places. Then jump directly to Google Maps or Waze."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:178
msgid "¿Para quién es?"
msgstr "Who is it for?"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:181
msgid "Tipos de usuario"
msgstr "User types"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:184
msgid "Locales"
msgstr "Locals"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:188
msgid "Visitantes"
msgstr "Visitors"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:192
msgid "Negocios"
msgstr "Businesses"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:199
msgid ""
"Ahorra tiempo decidiendo a dónde ir. Descubre nuevos lugares en tu comuna, "
"encuentra esa terraza perfecta para esta noche y comparte recomendaciones "
"con amigos en un toque."
msgstr ""
"Save time deciding where to go. Discover new spots in your comuna, find that"
" perfect terrace for tonight, and share recommendations with friends in one "
"tap."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:204
msgid ""
"Llega a Medellín con un mapa listo. Conoce qué zonas tienen la mejor vida "
"nocturna, cafés y comida imperdible—todo organizado por barrios reales."
msgstr ""
"Arrive in Medellín with a ready-to-use map. Know which areas have the best "
"nightlife, coffee spots, and must-try food—all organized by real "
"neighborhoods."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:209
msgid ""
"Entiende cómo se posiciona tu zona y qué experiencias rodean tu negocio. "
"Contáctanos para actualizar tu ficha o destacar tu lugar."
msgstr ""
"Understand how your area is positioned and what experiences surround your "
"business. Contact us to update your listing or get featured."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:219
msgid "Transparencia y Datos"
msgstr "Transparency & Data"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:226
msgid "¿De dónde vienen nuestros datos?"
msgstr "Where does our data come from?"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:229
msgid ""
"Agregamos información pública de Google Places, OpenStreetMap y "
"contribuciones directas. Verificamos y curamos cada ficha para asegurar "
"calidad."
msgstr ""
"We aggregate public information from Google Places, OpenStreetMap, and "
"direct contributions. We verify and curate each listing to ensure quality."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:236
msgid "Aviso importante"
msgstr "Disclaimer"

#: explorer/templates/about.html:239
msgid ""
"La información puede cambiar sin previo aviso. Horarios, precios y "
"disponibilidad deben confirmarse directamente con cada establecimiento. No "
"somos responsables por inexactitudes."
msgstr ""
"Information may change without notice. Hours, prices, and availability "
"should be confirmed directly with each venue. We are not responsible for "
"inaccuracies."

#: explorer/templates/about.html:249
msgid "Volver a explorar"
msgstr "Back to explore"

